reviewText: nieces & nephews in Philippines loved it!
Charlie has always been a favorite of mine. This is a wonderful colloction of his movies
The Kid is one of my favorite silent films I was disapointed because the original film score which enhances the movie was not used
This is a DVD of some of Charlie Chaplin movies. In Black and white. Charle Chaplin does some funny stuff.

I recently saw my first Chaplin movie and I was immediately hooked.  I think I have everything he has ever done now, including his autobiography.  He was an amazing artist and a very interesting man.  Not many people can make me laugh out loud, but some of his movies either just amaze me, or they make me cry laughing.  The DVD arrived on time and in perfect condition.
